<script type="text/javascript">
    (function($){
       $(function() {
	       $('video').each(function() {
		       $(this).bind('play', function(e) {
			       ga('all.send', 'event', 'Video', 'Play', $(e.currentTarget).attr('data-video-title'));
		       });
		       $(this).bind('ended', function(e) {
			       ga('all.send', 'event', 'Video', 'Finished', $(e.currentTarget).attr('data-video-title'));
		       });
	       }); 
               //Track Downloads
               $('a').filter(function() {
                   return this.href.match(/.​*\.(zip|mp3*|mp4*|mpe*g|pdf|docx*|pptx*|xlsx*|rar*​)(\?.*)?$/);
               }).click(function(e) {
                   ga('send','event', 'download', 'click', this.href);
               });

               //Track Mailto
               $('a[href^="mailto"]').click(function(e) {
                   ga('send','event', 'email', 'send', this.href);
                });
               
               //Track Outbound Links
               $('a[href^="http"]').filter(function() {
                   if (!this.href.match(/.​*\.(zip|mp3*|mp4*|mpe*g|pdf|docx*|pptx*|xlsx*|rar*​)(\?.*)?$/)){
                       if (this.href.indexOf('premiershiprugby.com') == -1) return this.href;
                   }
               }).click(function(e) {
                   ga('send','event', 'outbound', 'click', this.href);
               });
                                
               //Track Affiliates
               $('a').filter(function() {
                   if ('/out/'!=''){
                          return this.href.match(/(\/out\/)/);
                   }
               }).click(function(event) {
                          ga('send','event', 'affiliates', 'click', this.href);
               });
                   
               //Track Hashmarks
               $('a').filter(function() {
                   if (this.href.indexOf('premiershiprugby.com') != -1 || this.href.indexOf('://') == -1) return this.hash;
               }).click(function(e) {
                   ga('send','event', 'hashmark', 'click', this.href);
               });

           });
    })(jQuery);
    </script>
<script>
     (function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){
     (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o),
     m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m)
     })(window,document,'script','//www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js','ga');
     ga('create', 'UA-24386340-2', 'auto');
     ga('require', 'displayfeatures');
     ga('send', 'pageview');
     ga('create', 'UA-24386340-5', 'auto', 'all');
     ga('all.require', 'displayfeatures');
     ga('all.send', 'pageview');
    </script>
